      <title>伊朗大使在传呼机爆炸中受伤 威胁报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/iran-threatens-retaliation-after-ambassador-hurt-in-pager-blasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗大使在黎巴嫩境内传呼机和其他无线设备的爆炸事件中受伤，伊朗威胁要进行报复，这引发了人们对中东地区新一轮针锋相对暴力事件的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/iran-threatens-retaliation-after-ambassador-hurt-in-pager-blasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡车司机工会拒绝支持特朗普或哈里斯担任总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/teamsters-decline-to-endorse-trump-or-harris-for-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际卡车司机兄弟会拒绝支持总统候选人，这对试图争取工会工人支持的卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普来说都是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/teamsters-decline-to-endorse-trump-or-harris-for-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 19:17:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价升至每桶 70 美元 海湾国家央行跟随美联储降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gulf-central-banks-follow-fed-cut-as-oil-prices-drop-toward-70</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海湾地区政策制定者跟随美联储采取自新冠疫情爆发以来的首次降息举措，使这个能源丰富的地区暂时缓解了油价下跌的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gulf-central-banks-follow-fed-cut-as-oil-prices-drop-toward-70</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国取消对部分台湾进口产品的关税豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/china-scraps-tariff-exemptions-on-some-taiwan-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着北京方面在与台湾的关系日益紧张之际继续加大压力，中国将取消对从台湾进口的部分农产品的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/china-scraps-tariff-exemptions-on-some-taiwan-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 17:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非立法者支持统计办公室增加预算的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-lawmakers-back-statistics-office-plea-to-up-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非立法者支持国家统计局提出的将预算增加 2.94 亿兰特（1670 万美元）的请求，但决定权在财政部长伊诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-lawmakers-back-statistics-office-plea-to-up-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 17:17:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大限制移民 2025 年学生签证数量将下降 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/foreign-student-visas-in-canada-to-further-drop-by-10-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府正在采取更多措施减少移民，而加拿大已不堪人口爆炸性增长的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/foreign-student-visas-in-canada-to-further-drop-by-10-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 17:00:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚政府计划对中央银行进行“代际变革”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/colombia-government-plans-generational-change-for-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚政府认为，央行的政策是造成经济疲软的原因，希望通过任命具有“新”思想的年轻经济学家来改组央行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/colombia-government-plans-generational-change-for-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 16:07:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国成员要求以色列撤出巴勒斯坦领土</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/un-members-demand-israel-withdraws-from-palestinian-territories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国大会周三要求以色列撤出1967年占领的巴勒斯坦领土、停止在约旦河西岸的定居点并允许流离失所的巴勒斯坦人及其后代返回家园。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/un-members-demand-israel-withdraws-from-palestinian-territories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 16:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的保守党对手计划试图推动提前选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trudeau-s-tory-rival-plans-vote-to-try-to-trigger-an-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多下周可能会面临不信任投票，但在反对党拒绝立即举行选举的想法后，他似乎能够安然度过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trudeau-s-tory-rival-plans-vote-to-try-to-trigger-an-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 16:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩爆炸事件后，以色列称地区战争进入“新阶段”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/more-lebanon-pagers-explode-in-day-after-attack-blamed-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特宣布与地区伊斯兰组织的战争进入“新阶段”，并表示将把军队调往黎巴嫩边境，这表明人们长期以来对更大范围冲突的担忧可能很快就会成为现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/more-lebanon-pagers-explode-in-day-after-attack-blamed-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 14:37:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
